	ioctlsort: zero pad ioctl codes to 4 places.
	Zero padding the ioctl number will allow simple sorting via shell scripts.

	* linux/ioctlsort.c (main): Output ioctl codes zero padded.
	* linux/ioctlent.h: Regenerated.

