	* Makefile.am (srpm): New phony target.

	* Makefile.am (EXTRA_DIST): Add ChangeLog.
	($(srcdir)/ChangeLog): New target, replaces gen-changelog phony target.
	Put it inside [MAINTAINER_MODE].

